name: Observe -> Control Module 6,
description: Visually inspect the internal wiring and components of Control Module 6, especially at the input and output terminals (+ side), to check for disconnections or obvious physical faults., outcome='No observable internal faults were found in Control Switch 6 or any of the inspected cables. Both Control Output Cable (+) 6 and Control Output Cable (−) 6 have both their P and N ports connected, while Control Input Cable (+) 6 has only its P port connected and its N port disconnected; Control Input Cable (−) 6 has both P and N ports connected. No polarity inversions were detected.\nCurrent persistent circuit state [differences with the starting state]:\nNo circuit-level changes introduced by diagnostics.', precise_action_cost=60.0, cost_breakdown=[('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0)], simplified_outcome=None)] 
